data.description: Nestled amidst 2.630 acres of pristine land, this impeccable custom-built home invites you into a world of luxury. With an expansive 3,317 sq. ft of interior space, every corner of this property radiates meticulous craftsmanship and unparalleled attention to detail.  At the heart of this home is a gourmet kitchen that is every culinary enthusiast's dream. It boasts pristine quartz countertops, a sophisticated marble backsplash, top-tier stainless steel appliances, a bespoke built-in wine rack, and a breakfast bar ideal for quick meals or casual conversations. Adjacent is a flexible main-level guestroom, a grand formal dining area ready to host unforgettable gatherings, a cozy living room for moments of relaxation, and a sunlit sunroom that offers panoramic views of the surrounding greenery. A conveniently placed laundry area completes the main floor.  Venture to the second level to discover a lavish master suite, a sanctuary featuring a spa-like bathroom with slate floors and a sleek walk-in shower. Two amply-sized bedrooms, each boasting capacious walk-in closets and a shared bathroom with a stylish dual vanity, offer views of the sprawling estate.  Desend into the basement to discover a well-designed bedroom offering privacy and serenity, making it ideal for guests or family. In addition, there's a space conducive for work or study, an expansive family room, and an extra room adaptable to various uses. Heated floors ensure consistent warmth and comfort throughout this level, and an added section stands prepped for potential bathroom installation, tailored to fit your needs.  The residence's commitment to excellence extends outdoors. The eco-friendly geothermal heating system, heated garage catering to car enthusiasts, energy-efficient windows, and custom lighting add touches of luxury. The wraparound porch is the perfect vantage point to enjoy views of the vast 2.630 acres, while a custom-designed fire pit beckons for twilight gatherings under the stars.  Located in a sought-after locale, this estate seamlessly marries style, comfort, and nature's beauty. Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a slice of paradise; come and experience this architectural masterpiece today!  Conveniently located 4 minuets to the Air Force main gate.
